narratives.question_text: What knowledge, skills, and insights did you develop by taking this course?
comments: I got hands-on experience designing and implementing vacuum tube circuitry. Although vacuum tubes are essentially obsolete for many purposes, they have a special niche in music production and recording. In addition, the process of designing and building the circuits made me much more confident in circuit design in general, and gave me insights into how to analyze circuits from a practical perspective.

narratives.question_text: What are the strengths and weaknesses of this course and how could it be improved?
comments: Increase the teaching aspect of this experience a little bit!
The independent project is essentially as involved as you want it to be, above a minimum, which is great because I really cared about this project and made sure I was satisfied with the result.

narratives.question_text: Would you recommend this course to another student? Please explain.
comments: I absolutely recommend the advanced independent project to other students. It is a great time spent on something you really care about.
